#: Resources.resx
#, new
msgid "ToolTipGetLicense"
msgstr ""
"When your subscription license has expired, or you are using a new device, "
"you must fetch a license from the server. Provide the information here and "
"follow the instructions."

#. An additional tooltip part, that explains that if no card was entered, getting the license this way won't work so easily. [ToolTipGetLicenseNoCard]
#: Resources.resx
#, new
msgid "ToolTipGetLicenseNoCard"
msgstr ""
"Leave the last 4 digits empty if you didn't use a card or don't recall them."

